dct_title_s: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of Italy
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Prime meridian: Greenwich. Index on verso. In lower right corner: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of Italy. In lower left corner: Rand, McNally & Co.'s indexed atlas of the world map of Italy, copyright, 1898.
dct_publisher_sm: Chicago : Rand McNally & Co., Map Publishers and Engravers, 1914, c1912.
